<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/820406-how-has-this-book-changed-your-life-or">How has this book changed your life or your perspectives on love and life in general ?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_820406'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F1427.The_Zahir">like</a></span>

